# CONTACT ENRICHMENT RULES

Donor files are contact enrichment ONLY — not donation amounts.
Ed: "dont add donations. thats old" / "just phones emails"

## IS NULL GUARD — MANDATORY ON EVERY UPDATE

First source wins. NEVER overwrite existing data. Every SET clause must have IS NULL guard:

```sql
UPDATE raw.ncboe_donations d
SET cell_phone = s.phone
FROM staging.some_table s
WHERE d.cluster_id = s.cluster_id
  AND d.cell_phone IS NULL  -- ← NEVER REMOVE THIS
```

## SOURCE ORDER (process in this exact sequence)

1. DataTrust (JOIN on rnc_regid) — phones only
2. staging.winred_deduped → personal/business email + phones
3. staging.harris_cluster_contacts + harris_spouse_contacts
4. staging.budd_matches
5. staging.budd_forsyth_matches
6. staging.budd_guilford_matches
7. staging.budd_wake_matches
8. staging.trump_nc_matches
9. staging.ncgop_forsyth_matches
10. staging.apollo_matches ← BAD EMAIL GUARD: exclude jsneeden@msn.com on cluster 372171
11. staging.master_matches
12. staging.military_matches
13. staging.trump_rally_matches ← tag trump_rally_donor = TRUE only (no contact info)
14. staging.ncgop_2026_matches
15. staging.foxx_matches
16. staging.trump_ln_matches
17. staging.oneill_matches

## PHONE RULES

- Hierarchy (best → fallback): neustar+data_axle > data_axle > neustar > voter_file
- Clean: REGEXP_REPLACE(phone, '[^0-9]', '', 'g'), truncate to 10 digits
- Label: cell_phone vs home_phone — clearly distinguish

## EMAIL RULES

- Personal domains → personal_email:
  gmail, yahoo, hotmail, aol, icloud, msn, outlook, comcast, att, bellsouth, earthlink
- All other domains → business_email
- Ed: "clearly identify a label cell phone and personal email and business emails"

## CONTAMINATION BLACKLIST

